title: Mohan Dish
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Indian food that's not pure veg but does include around 7-10 vegetarian entree choices. Vegans need to inquire. Menu also offers salads, a few of which are vegan suitable (like the chickpea salad) or can be ordered without animal products. Directions: take Nanboku line to Asabu, and get off at Kita24 Jo subway station.
